Class PrefixMappingMonitor

PrefixMappingChanges
public class PrefixMappingMonitor extends Object implements org.apache.jena.shared.PrefixMapping
An implementation of PrefixMapping that is a wrapper for another PrefixMapping and also decomposes all changes to set/remove operations.
